      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking to find a new home for my car, and it\u2019s been such a fantastic ride for me. It's in really solid shape and has been super well-maintained\u2014honestly, it still drives like a dream and looks great too! It\u2019s been incredibly reliable, and I\u2019d love for it to go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come by and see it for yourself!",
