    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 996.2 Carrera is a mechanically sound example of Porsche\u2019s water-cooled evolution, featuring the 3.6L M96 flat-six engine equipped with VarioCam Plus for optimized valve timing across the rev range. The G96 6-speed manual gearbox provides tactile engagement, paired with a chassis that remains flat through corners thanks to a well-maintained multi-link rear suspension and MacPherson struts up front. Crucial preventative maintenance has been addressed, including an IMS bearing retrofit and a fresh Rear Main Seal (RMS) to ensure long-term reliability. The braking system utilizes four-piston aluminum monoblock calipers for exceptional heat dissipation and pedal feel. While the finish shows minor aerodynamic patina from regular road use, the structural and mechanical components are in excellent working order, making this a prime candidate for a dedicated driver\u2019s car.",
      "price": 34800.0,
