    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This 2018 Lexus RX 350 is a beautifully maintained example of luxury and dependability. The exterior is finished in a deep Obsidian Black that retains a high-gloss luster, showing only minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small, faint scratch near the trunk\u2014typical signs of careful use. Inside, the Parchment leather upholstery remains supple and free of cracks or tears, complemented by genuine wood trim that is still vibrant. As a non-smoker vehicle, the cabin is fresh and clean. Every feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the heated steering wheel and premium navigation system, operates exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health; it has a documented history of on-time dealership servicing, including a recent brake fluid flush and oil change. The transmission shifts seamlessly, and the engine runs whisper-quiet. With a clean title and tires showing deep tread, this SUV is a turn-key luxury experience ready for its next owner.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
